Note: Mixed positional and named arguments: positional args fill their declared
Note: positions in order, named args bind to their named slots.
Note: add3(10, 20, 3) with mixed: positional 10, named b as 20, positional 3
Note: -> a=10, b=20, c=3, sum=33
Note: Expected exit code: 33

Process called "add3" takes a as Integer, b as Integer, c as Integer returns Integer:
    Return a plus b plus c
End Process

Process called "main" returns Integer:
    Let r be add3 with 10, b as 20, 3
    Return r
End Process
